# CI/CD Flow After Configuring env Variables
    Step                                        Purpose
1. Set environment variables           Workflow, job, or step level
2. Checkout repository                 actions/checkout
3. Install dependencies                npm, maven, pip, gradle, etc.
4. Run tests                           unit, integration
5. Build your project                  create artifacts (build output)
6. Use env vars for configuration      API keys, URLs, versions
7. Deploy based on environments        dev/stage/prod
8. Notify / upload artifacts           Slack, Teams, artifact upload
